This test will check that transmission manage torrents correctly
<dl>
    <dt> Open transmission</dt>
        <dd>Transmission opens correctly</dd>
    <dt> Click on "Open a Torrent" button</dt>
        <dd>A new window appears</dd>
    <!-- unspecified parameter... there is not a prerequisit of having a torrent file. -->
    <dt>Select a torrent file</dt>
        <dd>The torrent starts to be downloaded</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Pause Torrent" button</dt>
        <dd>The torrent is paused</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Start Torrent"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent continues its download</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Properties"</dt>
        <dd>A new window should appear and you must see information about the torrent there.</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Remove Torrent", then agree to the pop up</dt>
        <dd>The torrent should disappear</dd>
    <dt>Open the "open a new torrent" dialogue box using the key combination: Ctrl+O</dt>
        <dd>It opens correctly</dd>
    <dt>Open the "open a new torrent URL" dialogue box using the key combination: Ctrl+U</dt>
        <dd>It opens correctly</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar and click on "View" and then choose different bars (Toolbar, Filterbar, Statusbar, Compact View)</dt>
        <dd>No issues are encounted</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar and click on "View" and later choose different Sorts (by Activity, by Age, by Name, by Progress,...)</dt>
        <dd>No issues are encounted</dd>
</dl>

<em>Depends on previous test</em>
This test will check that the Torrent menu Works
<dl>
    <dt>Open the transmission</dt>
        <dd>Transmission opens correctly</dd>
    <dt>Select a torrent and click on "Properties"</dt>
        <dd>You can see the properties interface</dd>
    <dt>Try to get the same result using the key-combination: Alt+Return</dt>
        <dd>You see the same interface as above</dd>
    <dt>Select a torrent and click on "Open Folder"</dt>
        <dd>A new window should appear and you will be in the torrent folder</dd>
    <dt>Select a torrent and stop it</dt>
    <dt>Select the same torrent and click on "Start"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent starts correctly</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Pause"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent pauses</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Start Now"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent starts correctly</dd>
    <dt>Try to get the same result using the key-combinations: Start(Ctrl+S), Pause(Ctrl+P) and Start Now(Shift+Ctrl+S)</dt>
        <dd>No issues are encounted</dd>
    <!-- UNVERIFIED STEP -->
    <dt>Add at least three torrents</dt>
    <dt>Click on "Queue" and try the options (Move to Top, Move Up, Move Down and Move to Bottom)</dt>
        <dd>No issues are encounted</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Set Location"</dt>
        <dd>A new interface appears and you can select a new folder</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Verify Local Data"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent verifies</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Remove"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent removes correctly</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Delete Files and Remove"</dt>
        <dd>The torrent and its files remove correctly</dd>
</dl>

<em>Depends on first test</em>
This test will check that the Help menu works
<dl>
    <dt>Open the transmission </dt>
        <dd>Transmission opens correctly</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar, click the "Help" menu and then "Message Log"</dt>
        <dd>A new interface should appear</dd>
    <dt>Go to "Level" and change the filter (information, error, debug)</dt>
        <dd>You can see the change has occured</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Pause"</dt>
        <dd>The buttons changes colour</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Save As"</dt>
        <dd>You can save the log correctly</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Clear"</dt>
        <dd>The list is now empty</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar, click the "Help" menu and then "Statistics"</dt>
        <dd>A new interface appears and you see a lot of information about your moves</dd>
    <dt>Click on "Reset"</dt>
        <dd>A confirmation message will appear after it, all your statistics will be reset</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar and click the "Help" menu and later "Donate"</dt>
        <dd>Your web browser will open the donation page of the Transmission project</dd>
    <dt>Press "F1"</dt>
        <dd>Your web browser will open the site about Transmission help</dd>
    <dt>Navigate main topics</dt>
        <dd>There are no issues with the content</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar, click the "Help" menu and then "Contents"</dt>
        <dd>The same content which was displayed in the previous step is shown</dd>
    <dt>Close the "transmission Help" window</dt>
        <dd>The main transmission window is displayed</dd>
    <dt>Go to the top bar, click the "Help" menu and then "About"</dt>
        <dd>A new "About transmission" window appears</dd>
    <dt>Press the "transmission Homepage" link</dt>
        <dd>Your web browser opens a valid URL</dd>
    <dt>Go back to the "About transmission" window</dt>
    <dt>Press the "Credits" button</dt>
        <dd>The interface shows credits</dd>
    <dt>Press the "License" button</dt>
        <dd>The interface shows a licence</dd>
</dl>

<strong>If all actions produce the expected results listed, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'passed' result.
    If an action fails, or produces an unexpected result, please <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> a 'failed' result and <a href="../../buginstructions">file a bug</a>. Please be sure to include the bug number when you <a href="results#add_result">submit</a> your result.</strong>
